author: pburba
msg: Follow-up to r28213, make svn_mergeinfo_parse() complain about empty ranges.
Relates to issue #3029 'Prevent mergeinfo with paths mapped to empty ranges'
(svn_mergeinfo_parse): Update doc string to account for new restriction.
(parse_revlist): Return an error if revlist is empty.  Add PATHNAME arg
allowing a more informative error message.
(svn_wc_canonicalize_svn_prop): Remove code that tested for empty
rangelist, the existing call to svn_mergeinfo_parse() handles that now.
